                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 351.117/93</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Bliss</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-08-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 26, 1916</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1557. Your 1673, August 25. Minister of War willing to have Garrot brought before
                    special medical board for examination as to fitness for further service but
                    desires to know to what regiment he is attached. Am endeavoring to obtain this
                    information.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bliss</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
